// globalSettings.filters.json — Manage Settings window, "Filters" tab
// (GlobalSettingsWindow.Filters.cs). Auto Filters trade/rule configuration UI:
// trades sidebar, rule list, rule editor (Filter Logic / Override Style /
// Appearance & Visibility), rule + trade edit popups, Templates popup, batch
// edit / merge tools.
//
// NOT localized (left as code):
//   - matchTypes dropdown items ("contains", "does not contain", "equals", …) —
//     these are stored directly as FilterRuleConfig.MatchType and compared with
//     == / switch elsewhere, so they are persisted logic tokens, not just labels.
//   - fill/line pattern name fallbacks ("Solid Fill", "Solid") — these must match
//     real Revit pattern names.
//   - single-glyph icon strings ("˅", "＋", "↑", "↓", "↺", "✕", "✓" via
//     ConvertFromUtf32) — decorative iconography, not language text.
//   - default export filename "LemoineAutoFilters.xml" — a filename, not a phrase.
